            "provider": "copilot-opus46",
            "locale": "en",
            "hint": "'But' expresses an unexpected result of a previous action — something different from what was anticipated.\nThe word `sincerely` highlights genuine effort, while `refused to forgive` is the unexpected rejection. Which conjunction conveys this disappointment?",
